Troubleshooting Tips
GitHub API Rate Limiting:

Unauthenticated requests limited to 10/minute
Add delays between requests (2-3 seconds)
Consider creating GitHub personal access token for higher limits
Check rate limit status: curl https://api.github.com/rate_limit
Censys API Errors:

Verify credentials in ~/.censys/credentials
Check API quota at https://censys.io/account
Free tier limited to 250 queries/month
Use specific queries to reduce API calls
Missing Dependencies:

pip3 install --upgrade requests censys
Permission Errors:

chmod +x *.py *.sh
Empty Results:

Verify internet connectivity
Check API credentials are valid
Ensure search queries are properly formatted
Review API documentation for query syntax
